{"tid":2413843,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"獸父逼10歲女兒穿情趣內衣　性侵590次！她隱忍6年最後希望仍落空","createTime":"2021-02-19T04:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T06:47:50.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1be4d9ab28e659c7d6cca56e19bfe1228747f37e","tid":2413843,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:09:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d9Ro1qP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd9Ro1qP.jpg&h=66803816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">台南</span>市一名狼父從2012年9月起趁妻子上大夜班，對當時只有10歲女兒伸狼爪，逼女兒穿<br />\n情趣內衣，對她使用情趣用品，最後性侵女兒，他以事情曝光，會導致「爸媽離婚」，逼<br />\n女兒不准聲張，女兒為此隱忍6年，直到狼父因詐欺罪遭警方羈押，少女才告訴學校輔導<br />\n老師，但其父母仍在2017年離婚，讓她的希望落空。檢警發現，狼父以每周兩次性侵女兒<br />\n，6年共590次，台南地院依強制性交罪判處12年。<br />\n <br />\n台南地院法官認為，被告沒有克制性衝動，為滿足一己色慾，罔顧人倫，多次性侵女兒，<br />\n不尊重女兒的身體自主權，造成身心受創並留下難以磨滅陰影，嚴重影響其人格發展的健<br />\n全，毀損被害人對兩性關係及家庭觀念認知，難以彌補的傷害。法官認為被告對未滿14歲<br />\n女子犯強制性交罪共590次，各處7年8月徒刑，應執行12年徒刑，全案可上訴二審。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20210218/7BAKIIQ6YBFIXDM5UB5R66HCHM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2F7BAKIIQ6YBFIXDM5UB5R66HCHM%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69NUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=e2f65428\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2F7BAKIIQ6YBFIXDM5UB5R66HCHM%2F&h=c2699e06\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20210218/7BAKIIQ6YBFIXDM5UB5R66HCHM/</a>"},{"pid":"6f976d5d46e0e1ae8c446d190bef5d15ad0ff913","tid":2413843,"uid":160668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:10:15.000Z","msg":"590/6<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb9f696c079a0f285dc01ec4395a191001490c4","tid":2413843,"uid":288797,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:28:27.000Z","msg":"數得出幾多次 好恐怖"},{"pid":"2ef4b35373707bdc7a64e4236dd525eb137770b3","tid":2413843,"ui